  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content">About us</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-blockcontent-value">
                <div class="field-content"><p>E<span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 15px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">ducation is universally recognized as one of the most fundamental building blocks for human development and reducing poverty. Our blog explores issues related to global education policy. </span></p></div>
  </div>
